Cell.Text: You got it. Horse, wagon and all. Plopped here without so much as a word. | I used to be one of the best traders in High Rock, you know. People would track me down just to see what I had for sale.

Node.Caption: DLC1SoulCairnMerchantStartTopic02: So that's how you got here.

Cell.Text: Very funny. | And what exactly are you going to pay me with? Take a look around. Gold doesn't exactly win you any friends around here.

Let's just say I sold something to a guy who turned out to work for a whole coven of necromancers. | How in the name of Zenithar was I to know the ingredients were phony? Do I look like someone that would double-cross a necromancer?
G|I might be just a soul now, but I'm still not going to give my stuff away. Bring me at least twenty-five husks and then we'll talk.
Sure, got plenty. What am I gonna' do with it?
Well, I've been so busy, I dunno. What are you, kidding me?
Of course I do. What do you want?
[S] G|A wondrous blade... ahhh, never mind. Just take the darn thing.
[S] G|I can't believe I'm trading this for some dried up plants. Oh well, a sale's a sale.
[S] G|Well, I hate to see it go, but what am I gonna do with it here anyway?
[S] G|Hope it gets you out of this place alive. Sure didn't do me much good.
[S] G|This won't stop your soul from getting ripped out, but at least you'll look good when your corpse hits the ground.
G|Oh sure, keep pestering me then, by all means.
G|No husks, no sale. Guess you have some scavenging to do.

I'll tell you what. I appreciate what you're trying to do, so I'll play along. | The only thing I see around here in abundance are soul husks. You know, those ugly fungus-looking things growing out of the ground. | Bring me a say... twenty-five of them, and you can rummage through what was left on my cart.

Node.Caption: DLC1SoulCairnMerchantStartTopic04: There must be something you want.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Sure. Here you go. Can't understand a word of it, maybe it will do you some good.

[S] Odds and ends I've gathered over the years. Well, used to gather before all of this nonsense happened to me. | Tell me what you're looking for and maybe we can make a deal... if you have the husks.

Node.Caption: DLC1SoulCairnMerchantStartTopic05: Fair enough. What do you have?
